sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Authenticated User
    participant TSE as TSE
    participant SM as Security Module
    participant Storage as Storage Medium

    Note over User: User is logged in<br/>(logger, admin or timeadmin)

    User->>TSE: logOut()
    activate TSE
    
    TSE->>TSE: Check: User authenticated?
    
    alt User not authenticated
        TSE-->>User: Exception:<br/>ErrorUserNotAuthenticated
    else User authenticated
        TSE->>SM: Create logOut System Log
        activate SM
        SM->>SM: Log Data:<br/>- eventTriggeredByUser<br/>- logoutResult
        SM->>SM: signatureCounter++
        SM->>SM: Create Signature
        SM-->>TSE: Log Message + Signature
        deactivate SM
        
        TSE->>Storage: Save logOut Log
        activate Storage
        Storage-->>TSE: OK
        deactivate Storage
        
        TSE->>TSE: Set User Status:<br/>UNAUTHENTICATED
        
        TSE->>TSE: Optional: Reset Auto-Logout Timer
        
        TSE-->>User: Logout successful
    end
    deactivate TSE
    
    Note over User,Storage: User is now logged out<br/>Access only to unauthenticated functions
